## Project Rules
- MCP tool definitions and result formatting live in `src/ui/server_ui.rs`
- The UI layer may call only the adapter layer
- The adapter layer coordinates core and PAL calls and should not contain Win32 unsafe code
- Template matching lives in `src/core/vision_core.rs`
- Win32 window and input operations live in `src/pal/`
- Unsafe Win32 calls stay isolated to PAL modules
- All numeric constants live in `src/state/`
- Windows-only dependencies stay under `[target.'cfg(windows)'.dependencies]`
- `rmcp` stays at the UI/server boundary
- Capture and click paths must bring the target window into a usable state before acting

